    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Multipart/Related content-type provides a common mechanism for representing objects that are aggregates of related MIME body parts.  This document defines the Multipart/Related content-type and provides examples of its use.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
